&lt;li&gt;Support sales opportunities by providing product information, roadmap updates, product samples, and price quotations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain awareness of and communicate internally to sales and marketing teams regarding major market trends, customer strategies, and competitive activity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;International business travel to support customer meetings as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate and collaborate with sales and marketing teams to resolve business issues, plan account strategies, product alignment and achieve revenue goals.&lt;/li&gt;
